{
  "stem": "5255.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were not as strong, strongly built like they would be in a big city.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they were made out of wood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't a big thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some of the boards were loose.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You could go in and out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if they caught you, it was-- it wasn't that bad in Plonsk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that's the reason I went in and out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was certain spots, nobody was there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that camp, after the people-- there were 10 people that died of typhus.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after they, the rest of them recuperated, they liquidated the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I could've gone any place I wanted to because I got a paper not listing me as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got a paper as I was liberated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I paid my dues to society because I was in that camp, and that I was released.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's all it stated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, I-- but I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't have any place to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went back to the ghetto in Plonsk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I went back to the ghetto in Plonsk, after being there for a few days, I went back to the family that gave me lodging.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they gave me lodging all over again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the local Jewish community, the administration, issued a edict or whatever that anybody that is here illegally, who does not belong to the community, that came from other places, like me, I came from Warsaw, we should register so we can get food stamps.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because without stamps, you had to buy everything on the black market.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But if you have legal residence and you get food stamps, the merchandise or the products that you buy, like bread or whatever else you need, provisions, costed very little.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
